Name: edeposit.amqp.ftp
Version: 1.0.2
Summary: E-Deposit's wrapper over ProFTPD.
Home-page: https://github.com/edeposit/edeposit.amqp.ftp/
Author: Edeposit team
Author-email: edeposit@email.cz
